    "updated_at": "2016-03-16T00:53:29Z",
    "body": "I had the same problem with rendering issues when trying to hide a webview using display:none, probably caused by the upstream issue mentioned above.\n\nTry hiding with with a style using \"width: 0px; height:0px;\" and avoid hidden and display:none. \n"
